<br>
I would suggest hanging onto the troll hide until you can get a Cat Belt, TBB or FBSS (in that order of preference for me anyway).  If you can get your paws on an FBSS it's still very nice to have and you can always use it as a very powerful trade item to get a BUNCH of items you need if you don't like being a death magnet <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I found the FBSS got me in far more trouble than it was worth so I wound up trading it off.  Using 9/19 weapons with haste songs and an FBSS got me far more attention from mobs than I ever wanted <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
